FBIS4-42043 "drsov126_m_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-126 Daily Report 29 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Russian Guards Return Fire From Afghan Territory Russian Guards Return Fire From Afghan Territory LD2906105794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0934 GMT 29 Jun 94 LD2906105794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] [Text] Dushanbe, 29 Jun -- At about 2300 on Tuesday a border detail in the sector of the 12th border outpost of the Moscow border detachment was subjected to intense shelling. The Russian border guards returned fire and neutralized the firing points. There were no casualties among the Russian border guards. An ITAR-TASS correspondent found this out from informed military sources in Dushanbe. This is already the third case this week of firing on Russian border guard detachments and border posts from Afghan territory.
